results.name: Number of ways to write n as n = u*v*w with 1<=u<=v<w.
comment: a(n) = 1 iff n prime or n prime^2: a(A000430(n))=1.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..2048
program: (PARI) A088433(n) = { my(s=0); fordiv(n, u, for(v=u, n-1, for(w=v+1, n, if(u*v*w==n, s++)))); (s); }; \\ _Antti Karttunen_, Aug 24 2017
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Oct 01 2003
